dc_description_s: This data layer represents public lands for Polk County in 2021.[The location of City Lands, County Lands, Conservancy Lands, Federal Lands, Town Lands, School District Lands, State Lands, and Village Lands within Polk County, Wisconsin.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://www.co.polk.wi.us/landinfogisdataportal
